{"word":"Ish-Bosheth","slug":"ish-bosheth","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Ish-Bosheth</b> <a href=\"#/H378\">H378</a> <br/> Son of Saul.<br/> Called Esh-Baal<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=8&verse=33'>1Ch 8:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=9&verse=39'>1Ch 9:39</a><br/> Made king by Abner<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=2&verse=10'>2Sa 2:10</a><br/> Deserted by Abner<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=3&verse=12'>2Sa 3:12</a><br/> Restores Michal, David's wife, to David<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=3&verse=16'>2Sa 3:16</a><br/> Assassinated<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=4&verse=8'>2Sa 4:8</a><br/> Avenged by David<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=4&verse=12'>2Sa 4:12</a>"}]}